{"title_page": "Sunny Leone", "text_new": "{{pp-blp|small=yes|expiry=indef}}\n{{short description|American Canadian actress}}\n{{redirect|Karenjit Kaur|the web series|Karenjit Kaur \u2013 The Untold Story of Sunny Leone}}\n{{distinguish|Sunny Lane}}\n{{EngvarB|date=January 2015}}\n{{Use mdy dates|date=October 2012}}\n{{Infobox adult biography\n| name         = Sunny Leone\n| image        = Sunny Leone for 'Sunny Ka New Year Call' campaign.jpg\n| caption      = Leone in 2020\n| birth_name   = Karenjit Kaur Vohra\n| birth_date   = {{Birth date and age|mf=yes|1981|5|13}}<ref name=OwnBio>{{cite web|url=http://www.sunnyleone.com/en/about|title=About Me|publisher=www.sunnyleone.com|accessdate=January 5, 2016}}</ref>\n| birth_place  = [[Sarnia, Ontario]], Canada<ref name=avn />\n| other_names  = Karen Malhotra\n| occupation   = Actress, former pornographic actress\n| years_active = 2001\u2013present\n| spouse       = {{marriage|Daniel Weber|2011}}<ref>{{cite web|url=http://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/entertainment/bollywood/news-interviews/Sunny-Leones-husband-comes-to-India/articleshow/12687162.cms/ |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140322071308/http://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/entertainment/bollywood/news-interviews/Sunny-Leones-husband-comes-to-India/articleshow/12687162.cms |url-status=dead |archive-date=March 22, 2014 |title=Sunny Leone's husband comes to India |work=Times of India |date=April 16, 2012 |accessdate=October 1, 2012 |df= }}</ref>\n| children     = 3\n| known_for    = [[Bigg Boss (Hindi season 5)|Bigg Boss 5]], [[Jism 2]], [[Ragini MMS 2]], [[Ek Paheli Leela]], [[Splitsvilla]]\n| citizenship  = {{hlist|Canada|United States|Overseas Citizen of India}}\n}}\n\n'''Karenjit Kaur Vohra''' (born May 13, 1981), known by her [[stage name]] '''Sunny Leone''' ({{IPAc-en|l|i|\u02c8|o\u028a|n|i}}), is a former [[pornographic actress]] currently active in the Indian film industry as an [[actress]] and [[model (person)|model]].<ref name=\"sunnyleone.com\">{{cite web|url=http://www.sunnyleone.com/en|title=Sunny Leone \u2013 Desi Porn \u2013 SunnyLeone.com|work=sunnyleone.com}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|title=Sunny Leone profile|url=http://www.avn.com/porn-stars/Sunny-Leone-274888.html|publisher=AVN|accessdate=Dec 27, 2015}}</ref> She has American and Canadian citizenship. She has also used the stage name '''Karen Malhotra'''.<ref>{{cite news|url=https://www.theglobeandmail.com/arts/film/a-sunny-day-in-sarnia/article4098311/|title=A Sunny day in Sarnia|publisher=|accessdate=July 16, 2016}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.santabanta.com/bollywood/51052/how-karen-malhotra-turned-into-a-world-famous-porn-star-sunny-leone/|title=How Karen Malhotra turned into a world-famous porn star Sunny Leone|publisher=|accessdate=July 16, 2016}}</ref> She was named ''[[Penthouse (magazine)|Penthouse]]'' [[List of Penthouse Pets of the Year|Pet of the Year]] in 2003, was a contract performer for [[Vivid Entertainment]], and was named by ''[[Maxim (magazine)|Maxim]]'' as one of the 12 top porn stars in 2010.\n\nShe has played roles in independent mainstream events, films, and television series. Her first mainstream appearance was in 2005, when she worked as a red carpet reporter for the [[MTV Video Music Awards]] on [[MTV India]]. In 2011, she participated in the Indian reality television series ''[[Bigg Boss (Hindi TV series)|Bigg Boss]]''. She also has hosted the Indian reality show ''[[MTV Splitsvilla|Splitsvilla]]''.\n\nIn 2012, she made her [[Bollywood]] debut in [[Pooja Bhatt]]'s [[erotic thriller]] ''[[Jism 2]]'' (2012) and shifted her focus to mainstream acting which was followed up with ''[[Jackpot (2013 film)|Jackpot]]'' (2013), ''[[Ragini MMS 2]]'' (2014), ''[[Leela (2015 film)|Ek Paheli Leela]]'' (2015) and ''[[Tera Intezaar]]'' (2017).\n\nApart from her acting career she has been part of activism campaigns including the [[Rock 'n' Roll Marathon Series|Rock 'n' Roll Los Angeles Half-Marathon]] to raise money for the [[American Cancer Society]] and has also posed for a [[PETA|People for the Ethical Treatment of Animals]] (PETA) ad campaign with a rescued dog, encouraging pet owners to have their cats and dogs spayed and neutered.\n\nSince 2011, Leone has been married to musician Daniel Weber.<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.dnaindia.com/entertainment/report-sunny-leone-s-husband-daniel-weber-also-a-porn-star-will-now-make-his-bollywood-debut-in-wife-s-jackpot-1874643|title=Sunny Leone's husband Daniel Weber, will now make his Bollywood debut in wife's 'Jackpot' \u2013 Latest News & Updates at Daily News & Analysis|date=August 15, 2013|publisher=|accessdate=July 16, 2016}}</ref>\nShe currently lives in [[Mumbai]], [[Maharashtra]].<ref name=\"NDTVGaneshChaturthi\" />\n\nSunny Leone has appeared in the Malayalam film [[Madhura Raja]] in 2019.\n\n== Early life ==\nKarenjit Kaur Vohra was born on May 13, 1981 in [[Sarnia, Ontario]] to [[Sikh]] [[Indian people|Indian]] [[Punjabi people|Punjabi]] parents.<ref>{{cite news|url=http://www.hindustantimes.com/entertainment/tabloid/sunny-leone-s-real-name-revealed/article1-847131.aspx|title=Sunny Leone's real name revealed!|accessdate=1 April 2014|newspaper=Hindustan Times|date=April 27, 2012|agency=Agencies|url-status=dead|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20140413142211/http://www.hindustantimes.com/entertainment/tabloid/sunny-leone-s-real-name-revealed/article1-847131.aspx|archivedate=April 13, 2014|df=mdy-all}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|author=Vickey Lalwani, Mumbai Mirror |url=http://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/entertainment/bollywood/news-interviews/People-in-India-are-conservative-Sunny-Leone/articleshow/23691999.cms? |title=People in India are conservative: Sunny Leone|work=Times Of India |date=August 8, 2013 |accessdate=Dec 27, 2015}}</ref><ref name=eyeweek/> Her father was born in [[Tibet]] and raised in [[Delhi]], while her mother (who died in 2008)<ref name=mompass>{{cite web |url=http://www.xbiz.com/news/news_piece.php?id=96058&mi=all&q=sunny+