/ref><ref name=torostar/> fulfilling her grandparents' dream that the family be together in one place.<ref name=eyeweek>{{cite news|url=http://eyeweekly.com/blog/post/32910 |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20081119075403/http://eyeweekly.com/blog/post/32910 |archivedate=November 19, 2008 |title=Sunny Leone's America |accessdate=July 4, 2008 |first=Marc |last=Weisblott |date=July 4, 2008 |work=[[Eye Weekly]] |url-status=dead |df=mdy }}</ref> She had her first [[kiss]] at 11,<ref name=brazzers/> lost her [[virginity]] at 16<ref name=brazzers/> with a [[basketball]] [[Player (game)|player]]<ref name=brazzers/> and discovered her [[bisexuality]] at 18.<ref name=bisexual>{{cite web |url=http://www.mensfitness.com/advice/hot-women/meet-girl-sunny-leone |title=Meet the Girl: Sunny Leone |accessdate=February 1, 2007 |date=February 1, 2007 |work=[[Men's Fitness]]}}</ref><ref name=brazzers>{{cite web|url=https://www.brazzers.com/profile/view/id/1213/sunny-leone/|title=Sunny Leone profile|accessdate=March 9, 2018|date=March 9, 2018|website=[[Brazzers]]}}</ref>\n\n==Pornographic career==\nBefore working in the [[porn]] [[industry]], she worked at a German bakery,<ref name=\"xrent\"/> a [[Jiffy Lube]],<ref name=\"Ambush\"/> and later a tax and retirement firm.<ref name=\"freeones.com\">{{cite web|url=http://blog.freeones.com/2007/08/06/exclusive-interview-with-sunny-leone|title=Exclusive Interview with Sunny Leone|accessdate=2007-08-06|author=freeones|date=2007-08-06|publisher=freeones}}</ref> She was also studying to become a nurse.<ref name=LATimes2016/>\n[[File:Sunny Leone r140014.png|thumb|left|upright|Leone at the 2002 [[AVN Adult Entertainment Expo]], one of her earliest promotional appearances|alt=A black-haired woman wearing a yellow top and jeans sitting behind a table looking up at the camera.]]\n\nWhen picking a name for her adult career, she has said that Sunny is her real name and Leone was picked by [[Bob Guccione]], former owner of ''Penthouse'' magazine.<ref name=\"adultfilm\"/> She posed for ''Penthouse'' magazine, and was named ''Penthouse'' Pet of the Month for the March 2001 issue, followed by a feature in the Holiday 2001 edition of ''[[Hustler]]'' magazine as a Hustler Honey. She has also appeared in other magazines including ''Cheri'',<ref name=\"Cheri\">{{cite web|url=http://business.avn.com/articles/Sunny-Leone-Featured-in-i-Cheri-i-27277.html|title=Sunny Leone Featured in Cheri|accessdate= 2007-08-28|author=Eddie Adams|date=2007-08-28|publisher=AVN}}</ref> '' Mystique Magazine'',<ref name=\"mystique\">{{cite web|url=http://www.mystique-magazine.com/bio/Sunny-Leone.html |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20071011052900/http://mystique-magazine.com/bio/Sunny-Leone.html |url-status=dead |archive-date=October 11, 2007 |title=Sunny Leone Jpg Pic Image & Video Gallery |accessdate=2008-08-26 |author=Mystique Magazine |publisher=Mystique Magazine |df= }}</ref> ''[[High Society (magazine)|High Society]]'', ''[[Swank (magazine)|Swank]]'', ''[[AVN (magazine)|AVN Online]]'', ''Leg World'', ''[[Club International]]'' and ''[[Lowrider Magazine|Lowrider]]'',<ref name=\"lowrider1\">{{cite web|url=http://www.lowridermagazine.com/models/0306_sunny_leone_lowrider_girl/index.html|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20070608210420/http://www.lowridermagazine.com/models/0306_sunny_leone_lowrider_girl/index.html|url-status=dead|archive-date=2007-06-08|title=Lowrider Model&nbsp;\u2014 Sunny Leone&nbsp;\u2014 June 2003 enter fold|accessdate=2003-06-01|author=Saul Vargas|date=2003-06-01|publisher=[[Lowrider Magazine]]}}</ref><ref name=\"lowrider2\">{{cite web|url=http://www.lowridermagazine.com/models/0311_sunny_leone_lowrider_girl/index.html|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20070525043822/http://www.lowridermagazine.com/models/0311_sunny_leone_lowrider_girl/index.html|url-status=dead|archive-date=2007-05-25|title=Lowrider Model&nbsp;\u2014 Sunny Leone&nbsp;\u2014 November 2003 Center Fold|accessdate=2003-11-01|auth