to the world of hardcore pornography, stating that she would only do lesbian scenes.<ref name=\"avn\"/> Her first movie released was titled ''Sunny''<ref>{{cite web|url=http://business.avn.com/articles/Vivid-to-Ship-i-Sunny-i-46475.html|title=Vivid to Ship Sunny|accessdate=2007-07-03|author=Dan Millar|date=2005-11-01|publisher=AVN}}</ref> and was released in December 2005. Her next movie, ''Virtual Vivid Girl Sunny Leone'', was the first interactive title for Leone, who was the first Vivid Girl to make such a movie.<ref name=\"vvivid\">{{cite web|url=http://business.avn.com/articles/Sunny-Leone-is-the-First-i-Virtual-Vivid-Girl-i-43328.html|title=Sunny Leone is the First Virtual Vivid Girl|accessdate=2006-04-05|author=AVN|date=2006-04-05|publisher=AVN}}</ref> Taking only four days to film,<ref\nname=\"xrent\">{{cite web|url=http://www.xrentdvd.com/Porn_Star_Interviews/Sunny_Leone.html|title=Inside Sunny Leone|accessdate=2007-06-07|author=Big D|date=2006-07-06|publisher=XRentDVD}}</ref> the movie won her her first [[AVN Award]] (Best Interactive DVD). She followed this with ''Sunny Loves Cher'', which featured her first on-screen [[female ejaculation|squirting]], and ''The Female Gardner'' co-starring Mikayla Mendez and [[Daisy Marie]].\n\nLeone's last two movies under her contract with Vivid were ''It's Sunny in Brazil'', which was filmed in [[Brazil]],<ref name=\"Brazil\">{{cite web|url=http://business.avn.com/articles/Vivid-Releases-i-It-s-Sunny-in-Brazil-i-25431.html|title=Vivid Releases It's Sunny in Brazil|accessdate=2007-05-10|author=AVN|date=2008-02-20|publisher=AVN|authorlink=AVN (magazine)}}</ref> and ''The Sunny Experiment'' also starring Monique Alexander and Brea Lynn.<ref name=\"experiment\">{{cite web|url=http://business.avn.com/articles/28879.html|title=Sunny Leone Performs The Sunny Experiment|accessdate=2007-12-19|author=Eddie Adams|date=2007-12-19|publisher=AVN}}</ref> The movies were released in October and December 2007 respectively.\n\nIn May 2007, upon re-signing her contract with [[Vivid Entertainment|Vivid]] for another six films, Leone agreed to perform for the first time with men on camera, but exclusively with her fianc\u00e9, Matt Erikson.<ref>{{cite web|url=http://business.avn.com/articles/4035.html |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20090622101812/http://business.avn.com/articles/4035.html |url-status=dead |archive-date=June 22, 2009 |title=Sunny Leone Renews Vivid Contract, Will Perform with Men |accessdate=2007-05-13 |author=David Sullivan |date=2007-05-13 |publisher=AVN |df= }}</ref> That summer she also received [[breast implant|breast augmentation]],<ref name=onset>{{cite web|url=http://business.avn.com/articles/5093.html |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20090923224755/http://business.avn.com/articles/5093.html |url-status=dead |archive-date=September 23, 2009 |title=On the Set: Sunny Loves Matt |accessdate=2008-03-21 |author=Jared Rutter |date=2007-08-31 |publisher=AVN |df= }}</ref> and shot her first movie under the new contract titled ''Sunny Loves Matt''. The movie led to her being nominated for three (out of six) AVN awards in 2009 in addition to being a choice for Female Performer of the Year.<ref name=\"awards09\">{{cite web|url=http://www.avnawards.com/pdf/2009_AVN_NOMINATIONS_11_25_08.pdf |format=PDF |title=NOMINATIONS 2009 AVN Adult Movie Awards |accessdate=2008-11-25 |author=AVN |date=2008-11-25 |publisher=AVN |authorlink=AVN (magazine) |url-status=dead |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20081203003734/http://www.avnawards.com/pdf/2009_AVN_NOMINATIONS_11_25_08.pdf |archivedate=December 3, 2008 }}</ref> She followed up her first boy-girl title with ''The Other Side of Sunny'' in October 2008, which would be the last time she would perform with Erikson.\n\nIn January 2008, Leone revealed that she was no longer exclusive to Erikson, and had done scenes with other actors, most notably [[Tommy Gunn (porn actor)|Tommy Gunn]], [[Charles Dera]], [[James Deen]]<ref name=\"sunlust\">{{cite web|url=http://www.xbiz.com/news/news_piece.php?id=97782|title=Sunny Leone Forms Her Own Studio, SunLust Pictures|accessdate=2008-08-22|author=Steve Javors|date=2008-08-22|publisher=[[XBIZ]]|url-status=dead|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20090601040441/http://www.xbiz.com/news/news_piece.php?id=97782|archivedate=June 1, 2009|df=mdy-all}}</ref> and Voodoo.<ref name=\"Tommygunn\">{{cite web|url=http://www.hotvideo.fr/component/video-star-du-x/2008_06_26/interview-de-sunny-leone-de-los-angeles-2008|title=Sunny Leone|accessdate=2008-06-26|author=Par G\u00e9rome Lorenzo|date=2008-06-26|publisher=Hot Video|url-status=dead|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20091224115725/http://www.hotvideo.fr/component/video-star-du-x/2008_06_26/interview-de-sunny-leone-de-los-angeles-2008|archivedate=December 24, 2009|df=mdy-all}}</ref>\n\nIn 2009, Vivid released her only movie performing with other male actors titled \"''Sunny B/G Adventure''\".<ref name=\"bgadventure\">{{cite news | url=http://www.xcritic.com/review/34909/sunny-leone-sunnys-bg-adventure/ | work=XCritic | first=Don | last= Houston | title=Sunny's B/G Adventure | date=December 29, 2009 | accessdate=}}</ref> Her final release under contract with Vivid \u2013 \"''Undress Me''\", once again made her exclusive to performing with just one male actor, Daniel Weber, who subsequently became her husband.<ref name=\"undress\">{{cite news | url=http://business.avn.com/articles/video/Sunny-Leone-Says-Undress-Me-342026.html | work=AVN | first=Nelson | last=X| title=Sunny Leone Says 'Undress Me' | date=June 5, 2009| accessdate=}}</ref>\n[[File:Sunny Leone at Exxxotica 2009 Miami Friday 2 adjusted.jpg|thumb|Sunny Leone at Exxxotica 2009 Miami]]\nIn August 2009, she announced the launch of her own studio, Sunlust Pictures, with Daniel Weber as her partner.<ref name=\"sunlustpartner\">{{cite web|url=http://www.xbiz.com/news/news_piece.php?id=98989&mi=all&q=sunny+leone|title=Sunny Leone Launches SunLust Pict