2008 |title=2008 Porn's Hot 100 |accessdate=2008-03-11 |author=Genesis Magazine |date=2008-03-11 |publisher=[[Genesis (magazine)|Genesis]] |df= }}</ref> number 34 on Desiclubs.com's Top 50 Coolest Desis of 2004,<ref name=\"50desi\">{{cite web|url=http://www.desiclub.com/community/culture/culture_article.cfm?id=200|title=DesiClub.com's Top 50 Coolest Desis of 2004|accessdate=2004-08-22|author=Peta Cooper|date=2004-08-22|publisher=desiclub.com|url-status=dead|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20050308072904/http://www.desiclub.com/community/culture/culture_article.cfm?id=200|archivedate=March 8, 2005|df=mdy-all}}</ref> and one of the \"40 under 40\" ranking on ''AVN Online'' magazine.<ref name=\"4040AVN\">{{cite web|url=http://www.nxtbook.com/syg/AVNONLINE/August2007/index.php?startpage=1 |title=AVN Online 40 under 40 |accessdate=2007-01-07 |author=AVN |date=2007-07-01 |publisher=AVN |url-status=dead |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20090108172507/http://www.nxtbook.com/syg/AVNONLINE/August2007/index.php?startpage=1 |archivedate=January 8, 2009 }}</ref> In 2010, she was named by [[Maxim (magazine)|''Maxim'']] as one of the 12 top female stars in porn.<ref name=MaxinTop10>{{cite web |url=http://business.avn.com/articles/video/Maxim-U-K-Names-Top-12-Porn-Stars-400571.html |title=Maxim U.K. Names Top 12 Porn Stars |work=business.avn.com |date=2010-06-18 |accessdate=2011-05-08}}</ref> She was voted number 82 in the Top 99 Women for 2012 in [[AskMen]].com's list.<ref name=\"Askmen2012\">{{cite web |url=http://www.askmen.com/specials/2012_top_99/82-sunny-leone.html |title=Top 99 Women |year=2012 |publisher=AskMen.com |accessdate=June 6, 2012}}</ref>\n\nIn 2013, she announced her retirement from the adult industry stating  \"I am lucky that the audience is accepting me. I have come my way from there (porn industry). I don't have any plans as of now to go back there.\"<ref name=retire>{{cite web |url=http://www.mtvindia.com/blogs/parent/urban-cupid/leone-announces