in the business world.<ref name=\"fox\">{{cite web|url=http://business.avn.com/articles/31210.html|title=Fox Reality Channel Launches 'My Bare Lady 2'|accessdate=2008-10-07|author=David Sullivan|date=2008-10-07|publisher=AVN}}</ref> In addition to filming her scene for ''Debbie Does Dallas'' in 2007, Leone was also part of a [[Showtime (TV network)|Showtime]] documentary of the same name detailing the production of the movie and the personal lives of its stars.\n\nShe indicated that for the right price she would seriously consider a career in [[Bollywood]].<ref name=\"steami\">{{cite web|url=http://www.steami.net/girls/sunny-leone-talks-about-bollywood-sex-indian-fans|title=Sunny Leone Talks About Bollywood, Sex & Indian Men|accessdate=2008-06-06|author=Steami.net|date=2008-01-01|publisher=Steami.net|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20080916084215/http://www.steami.net/girls/sunny-leone-talks-about-bollywood-sex-indian-fans/|archive-date=September 16, 2008|url-status=dead|df=mdy-all}}</ref> She was courted by Indian directors in the past but felt uncomfortable with the roles that she would have played.<ref name=\"adultfilm\">{{cite web|url=http://www.adultfilmdatabase.com/Interviews/2.cfm|title=Adultfilmdatabase Interviews: Sunny Leone Interview \u2013 11/06/2006|accessdate=2006-06-11|author=Adult Film Database|date=2006-06-11|publisher=[[Adult Film Database|AFDB]]}}</ref><ref name=\"royal\">{{cite web|url=http://www.royalmag.net/index.php?option=com_content&view=article&id=60|title=Sunny Leone|accessdate=2008-06-06|author=Royal Magazine|date=2008-01-01|publisher=Royal Magazine|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20090604165500/http://www.royalmag.net/index.php?option=com_content&view=article&id=60|archive-date=June 4, 2009|url-status=dead|df=mdy-all}}</ref> Director [[Mohit Suri]] reportedly asked Leone to play the lead role in his film ''[[Kalyug (2005 film)|Kalyug]]'', but instead cast [[Deepal Shaw]] as he could not afford Leone's $1&nbsp;million acting fee.<ref name=\"Kalyug\">{{cite web|url=http://www.desipowerchat.com/bollywood/a99_kalyugthefilm/kalyug_pictures_previews.htm|title=Kalyug the film Synopsis previews|accessdate=2008-06-06|author=Desipowerchat.com|publisher=Desipowerchat.com|url-status=dead|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20070810165226/http://www.desipowerchat.com/bollywood/a99_kalyugthefilm/kalyug_pictures_previews.htm|archivedate=August 10, 2007|df=mdy-all}}</ref> She has mentioned that [[Aamir Khan]] is her favorite Bollywood actor,<ref name=\"curry\">{{cite web|url=http://www.currybear.com/wordpress/?p=1713|title=Curry Bear Interviews \u2013 #1 Desi Porn Star Sunny Leone|accessdate=2008-06-10|date=2008-06-10|publisher=Curry Bear.com}}</ref> and that over 60% of her fans are from South Asia.<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.wrestlinginc.com/wi/girls/2010/3/sunny-leone/ |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20100305052146/http://www.wrestlinginc.com/wi/girls/2010/3/sunny-leone/ |url-status=dead |archive-date=March 5, 2010 |title=Sunny Leone Photo Gallery & Bio |publisher=www.wrestlinginc.com |accessdate=2010-03-11 |df= }}</ref>\n\nIn 2008, Leone announced that she would be starring in a mainstream action adventure movie titled ''Pirates Blood'', which was shot in [[Oman]]. The shooting was completed in two weeks and was to be released in winter 2008.<ref name=\"oman\">{{cite web|url=http://business.avn.com/articles/8327.html |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20091224164831/http://business.avn.com/articles/8327.html |url-status=dead |archive-date=December 24, 2009 |title=Sunny Leone to Appear in Bollywood Film |accessdate=2008-04-02 |author=Peter Warren |date=2008-04-02 |publisher=AVN |df= }}</ref> Leone also landed a role in ''[[Middle Men (film)|Middle Men]]'', producer Chris Mallick's indie feature about the birth of the online porn industry set for wide theatrical release in 2009.<ref name=\"middlemen\">{{cite web|url=http://business.avn.com/articles/33225.html|title=Sunny Leon